### Multi-Agent Wrapper Demo with SessionId

# Math Agent - with custom sessionId
POST http://localhost:7071/api/mathagent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is 5 squared?",
  "sessionId": "math-demo-123"
}

